    "id": "5a34a8c5-2785-4796-90d4-c3b7879c0114",
    "title": "ses",
    "content": "<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd\">\n<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /><style type=\"text/css\">\np, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }\nhr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }\nli.unchecked::marker { content: \"\\2610\"; }\nli.checked::marker { content: \"\\2612\"; }\n</style></head><body style=\" font-family:'Inter','Segoe UI','sans-serif'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Perfect \ud83d\udc4d\ud83d\udc0d<br />Now let\u2019s explain </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">PYTHON MEMORY</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">only from Python\u2019s point of view</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">, very </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">slow</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">, </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">deep</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">, and </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">simple</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">, using the </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">same mental model you already built</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">I\u2019ll explain </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">what goes into RAM</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">, </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">where Python puts things</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">, and </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">why Python feels different from C/Java</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">\ud83e\udde0 FIRST \u2014 PYTHON VIEW OF MEMORY (UNDERLINE THIS)</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Python sees memory as OBJECTS and REFERENCES.</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br />It does </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">not</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"> think in terms of \u201cvariables storing values\u201d.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">\ud83e\udde9 BIG PICTURE \u2014 PYTHON PROCESS MEMORY</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">When a Python program runs, RAM is used like this \ud83d\udc47</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">RAM</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u251c\u2500\u2500 Code Area        (Python bytecode)</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u251c\u2500\u2500 Stack (Frames)   (function calls, local names)</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u251c\u2500\u2500 Heap             (ALL Python objects)</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u2514\u2500\u2500 Internals        (GC, reference counts, caches)</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Everything is still RAM \u2014 Python just </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">organizes it</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">1\ufe0f\u20e3 CODE AREA (PYTHON BYTECODE) \ud83d\udcdc</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">When you write:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a = 10</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">print(a)</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Python does NOT execute text directly.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">It converts code into </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">bytecode</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">LOAD_CONST 10</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">STORE_NAME a</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">LOAD_NAME a</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">PRINT</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83d\udccc This bytecode lives in </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">memory</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br />\ud83d\udccc Read-only during execution</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Python executes </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">bytecode</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">, not source code.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">2\ufe0f\u20e3 STACK (CALL STACK &amp; FRAMES) \ud83d\udce6</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Python stack stores </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">frames</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">, not raw variables.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Each frame contains:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">local names</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">references to objects</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">instruction pointer</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Example:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">def f():</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">    x = 10</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">    g()</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">def g():</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">    y = 20</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">f()</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">https://youtu.be/9QXCkMTbrSk?si=z0NGJKri0sbLJhcz</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Stack while running </span><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">g()</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">TOP</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u2502 g frame     \u2502 y \u2192 20</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u251c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2524</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u2502 f frame     \u2502 x \u2192 10</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u251c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2524</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u2502 main frame  \u2502</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">BOTTOM</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83d\udccc Stack stores </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">NAMES \u2192 OBJECT references</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">, not objects.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">3\ufe0f\u20e3 HEAP (WHERE ALL OBJECTS LIVE) \ud83c\udfe0</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Every Python object lives in the HEAP.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Examples:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">int</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">str</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">list</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">tuple</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">dict</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">function</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">class</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a = [1, 2, 3]</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Memory:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">STACK (frame)</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a \u2500\u2500\u2500\u25b6 0xAAA</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">HEAP</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">0xAAA \u2192 list object [1,2,3]</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83d\udccc Objects never live on the stack in Python<br />\ud83d\udccc Stack only holds references</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">4\ufe0f\u20e3 WHAT A PYTHON OBJECT CONTAINS \ud83e\uddf1</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Each object has:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">type info</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">reference count</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">actual data</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Conceptually:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Object</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u251c\u2500\u2500 ref_count</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u251c\u2500\u2500 type pointer</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u2514\u2500\u2500 value/data</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Example (int):</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Object 10</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u251c\u2500\u2500 ref_count = 2</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u251c\u2500\u2500 type = int</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u2514\u2500\u2500 value = 10</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">5\ufe0f\u20e3 REFERENCE COUNTING (VERY IMPORTANT)</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Python keeps objects alive using </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">reference counting</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a = 10</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">b = a</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">10.ref_count = 2</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">When references go away:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">del a</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">del b</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">10.ref_count = 0 \u2192 object destroyed</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83d\udccc This is why Python knows </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">when to free memory</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">6\ufe0f\u20e3 IMMUTABLE VS MUTABLE (MEMORY EFFECT)</span></h2>\n<h3 style=\" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Immutable objects</span></h3>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">int</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">str</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">tuple</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a = 10</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a = 20</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Memory:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">10 (unchanged)</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">20 (new object)</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a moved</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u2714 object never changes<br />\u2714 name rebinds</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h3 style=\" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Mutable objects</span></h3>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">list</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">dict</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">set</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a = [1,2]</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a.append(3)</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Memory:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">same list object modified</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\u2714 object changes<br />\u2714 references stay same</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">7\ufe0f\u20e3 FUNCTION ARGUMENTS (PASSING MEMORY)</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Python passes </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">COPY OF REFERENCE</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">def change(x):</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">    x.append(3)</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">lst = [1,2]</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">change(lst)</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Memory:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">lst \u2500\u2510</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">     \u251c\u2500\u2500\u25b6 [1,2]</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">x \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Mutation affects caller.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">But:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">def change(x):</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">    x = [9,9]</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Memory:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">lst \u2500\u2500\u2500\u25b6 [1,2]</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">x \u2500\u2500\u2500\u25b6 [9,9]</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Caller untouched.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">8\ufe0f\u20e3 GLOBALS &amp; MODULE MEMORY \ud83c\udf0d</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">PI = 3.14</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Stored in:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">module namespace (dictionary)</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">lives for entire program</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">globals() \u2192 {'PI': 3.14, ...}</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">9\ufe0f\u20e3 GARBAGE COLLECTION (CYCLES) \u267b\ufe0f</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Reference counting cannot handle cycles:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a = []</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">a.append(a)</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Python uses a </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">cycle detector</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"> to clean these.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83d\udccc GC runs occasionally<br />\ud83d\udccc Stack objects are NOT GC\u2019d<br />\ud83d\udccc Heap objects ARE GC\u2019d</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">\ud83e\udde0 WHY PYTHON MEMORY FEELS \u201cMAGICAL\u201d</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Because:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">no pointers shown</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">no malloc/free</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">no manual cleanup</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">names instead of boxes</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">But internally:<br />\u2714 addresses exist<br />\u2714 heap exists<br />\u2714 stack exists</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Python just </span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">hides it</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">\ud83e\udde0 COMPLETE PYTHON MEMORY FLOW (FINAL)</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Source Code</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">   \u2193</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Bytecode (RAM)</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">   \u2193</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Stack Frames (names \u2192 references)</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">   \u2193</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Heap Objects (real data)</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">   \u2193</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Reference Counting + GC</span></p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">\ud83c\udfc6 FINAL GOLD SUMMARY (UNDERLINE THIS)</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Python stack stores names.</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Python heap stores objects.</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Variables are just references.</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Assignment rebinds names.</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Mutation changes objects.</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"><br /></span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">GC frees unused objects.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">\ud83d\udc8e ONE-LINE FINAL TRUTH</span></h2>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Python does not move values around \u2014 it moves references and mutates objects.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">If you want next \ud83d\ude80<br />\u2022 how Python stores lists internally<br />\u2022 why </span><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">id()</span><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\"> changes<br />\u2022 Python bytecode walkthrough<br />\u2022 memory diagrams interviewers love</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16pt; color:#000000;\">Just tell me \ud83d\ude04</span></p></body></html>",
